{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"51e6b16296","title":"谢镗忠传达全军文革小组的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"adbe480202","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":23,"articleId":"51e6b16296"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"6f7a683373","name":"军队和军事","type":"主题"},{"id":"70f74b01a1","name":"谢镗忠","type":"人物"},{"id":"714adabb18","name":"夺权和一月革命","type":"主题"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"d894956dbb","name":"谢镗忠"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"418e462860","type":"title","text":"谢镗忠传达全军文革小组的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"51e6b16296"},{"id":"0ab4bf7082","type":"paragraph","text":"〖说明：1月29日晚，防化学院105革命造反团等革命组织采取革命行动，夺取了防化学兵学院、防化学兵部等单位的党政财权，暂时控制军权，并上级军委批示。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"51e6b16296"},{"id":"0508a66715","type":"paragraph","text":"你们夺了防化学兵学院的权，这种革命精神我们是支持你们的。防化学兵部是军事领导机关，不要采取群众夺权的办法，你们可以自动撤出，不必作检讨了。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"51e6b16296"},{"id":"540aa7289d","type":"paragraph","text":"不能利用全军文革的意见打击左派，如果利用这个机会打击左派，就要犯错误，就要违反毛主席的教导。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"51e6b16296"},{"id":"6fca381280","type":"paragraph","text":"（总字664部队红联革命造反团）","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"51e6b16296"}],"page":{"id":"7597f8559f","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"51e6b16296","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}